<!-- Purpose:To test the Paragraph tag with the ALIGN element. -->

<!-- Expected result: The text below should be displayed in three paragraphs. Each paragraph is separated by the P tag.  The text will be center aligned.-->

<title>XHTML Functional -- P - ALIGN=center</title>

</head>

<body>

<p align="center">This is the first paragraph, at the very

beginning of this sample. This paragraph should be center

aligned.</p>

<p align="center">This is the second paragraph, at the middle of

this sample. When rendered by a browser, it will begin slightly

below the end of the first paragraph. This paragraph should be

center aligned.</p>

<p align="center">This is the third paragraph, at the end of this

sample. When rendered by a browser, it will begin slightly below

the end of the second paragraph. This paragraph should be center

aligned.</p>

</body>

